---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-editorial/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Tax Strategy | Strategic Insight Advisory"
  description="Strategic Insight Advisory's tax strategy service — deep-dive detail page."
  active="services"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-editorial/services/tax-strategy"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-section-padding pb-section-padding bg-surface overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-si-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter items-center">
<div class="relative z-10">
<div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
<div class="w-12 h-px bg-secondary"></div>
<span class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-secondary tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Services / Tax Strategy</span>
</div>
<h1 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-primary mb-8 leading-tight">
                        Navigating Complexity <br/>with Confidence.
                    </h1>
<p class="font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg mb-10">
                        In an era of shifting global regulations and intricate financial landscapes, simple compliance isn't enough. We provide the strategic pathing needed to mitigate risk and unlock value.
                    </p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<button class="bg-secondary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                            Consult with an Expert
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative h-[600px] hidden lg:block">
<!-- Path Art Simulation -->
<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 600 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path class="path-line" d="M100 100 C 300 100, 300 300, 500 300 S 500 500, 100 500" stroke="#d2c2cd" stroke-width="1"></path>
<rect fill="#a23f00" height="10" transform="rotate(45 100 100)" width="10" x="95" y="95"></rect>
<rect fill="#fdbb24" height="10" transform="rotate(45 500 300)" width="10" x="495" y="295"></rect>
<rect fill="#300033" height="10" transform="rotate(45 100 500)" width="10" x="95" y="495"></rect>
</svg>
<!-- Floating Data Points -->
<div class="absolute top-20 right-10 bg-white border border-outline-variant p-8 w-64 shadow-sm">
<span class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-secondary block mb-2 uppercase">Core Metric</span>
<div class="font-si-display-lg text-si-headline-lg text-primary">84%</div>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Reduction in tax liability through strategic restructuring.</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-20 left-40 bg-primary p-8 text-on-primary w-56">
<span class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-secondary-fixed-dim block mb-2 uppercase">Active Insight</span>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md">Global regulatory tracking for over 45 jurisdictions.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- The Methodology Section (Bento Grid / Process) -->
<section class="py-section-padding bg-surface-container-low border-y border-outline-variant">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-si-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-24">
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg text-primary mb-4">Our Methodology</h2>
<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative">
<!-- Connector Line for Desktop -->
<div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-0 w-full h-px bg-outline-variant z-0"></div>
<!-- Step 1 -->
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white border border-outline rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-8 hover:border-secondary transition-colors duration-500 group">
<span class="font-si-display-lg text-si-headline-md text-outline group-hover:text-secondary">01</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Discovery</h3>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">We dive deep into your current financial structures, identifying hidden risks and overlooked opportunities.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 2 -->
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white border border-outline rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-8 hover:border-secondary transition-colors duration-500 group">
<span class="font-si-display-lg text-si-headline-md text-outline group-hover:text-secondary">02</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Diagnosis</h3>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Analyzing the gap between current performance and future tax-optimized potential.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 3 -->
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white border border-outline rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-8 hover:border-secondary transition-colors duration-500 group">
<span class="font-si-display-lg text-si-headline-md text-outline group-hover:text-secondary">03</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Strategy</h3>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Crafting a bespoke roadmap that balances regulatory compliance with high-growth initiatives.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 4 -->
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-4xl" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Execution</h3>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Seamless implementation supported by continuous monitoring and reporting.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Core Service Pillars (Asymmetric Layout) -->
<section class="py-section-padding bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-si-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-gutter">
<div class="lg:w-1/3 pt-8">
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg text-primary mb-8 leading-tight">Focus Areas in Tax Strategy</h2>
<p class="font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12">
                            Our team of path-finders specializes in the most complex intersections of business and regulation.
                        </p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-outline-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="public">public</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-label-lg font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">International Taxation</h4>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Structuring cross-border transactions for maximum efficiency and minimum exposure.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-outline-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="account_balance">account_balance</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-label-lg font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">M&amp;A Strategy</h4>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Tax-optimized due diligence and integration for mergers and acquisitions.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="science">science</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-label-lg font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">R&amp;D Credits</h4>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Identifying and securing innovation-based incentives and credits.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-12 lg:pt-0">
<div class="relative bg-white border border-outline-variant p-0 group overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-64 relative overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="A professional accountant sitting at a clean, white minimalist desk with a dual-monitor setup, reviewing complex financial charts and tax documents. The lighting is bright and modern, with a palette of deep plums and warm oranges reflecting a corporate light-mode aesthetic." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBdQjMIHWKjrQS8Fb-aYkNkZQDmxwAPrzMe9hFhaY0njbbwV5na8uAZidvRvf7MQqQenlPy6LKbQ76ceK12Zxu1Bdq80aldCXi5lM6rDpMxtkm2T_nUTkUDcTEjVSDVjYwkPhZHHixvaEaQydfCtuN0Ubx0UlZN_oBqOO4oq_nvuaqawgoGzLz4iW7Pq3sDjxh1eTIjboY9HavbWlGoGrmKvwmfIAfRIJPkmafSXukUZHKxBxYQ9dC2fE8V95U-TdUjS6WRUQlY5tK6"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity"></div>
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<div class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-secondary mb-2 uppercase">Case Study</div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Optimizing the Global Supply Chain</h4>
<p class="font-si-body-md text-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-6">How we saved a mid-market manufacturing firm $4M in annual tax exposure.</p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="/templates/accounting-editorial/knowledge-hub">
                                    READ MORE <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2 text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative bg-primary p-12 text-on-primary flex flex-col justify-end min-h-[500px]">
<div class="absolute top-12 right-12 opacity-20">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl" data-icon="navigation">navigation</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-sm italic mb-6">"Their strategic guidance turned our tax function from a cost-center into a value-driver."</h4>
<p class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-secondary-fixed-dim uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">— CFO, Global Logistics Corp</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-section-padding relative overflow-hidden">
<!-- Geometric Path Art Background -->
<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-10" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 1440 600">
<path d="M-100 300 Q 300 100 720 300 T 1540 300" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"></path>
</svg>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-si-margin-desktop text-center relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg mb-8">Ready to find <br/>your path?</h2>
<p class="font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg mb-12 opacity-80">
                    Connect with our lead strategists to begin your diagnostic phase and discover the untapped potential in your financial ecosystem.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
<button class="bg-secondary text-on-primary px-12 py-5 font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-xl">
                        Schedule a Consultation
                    </button>
<button class="border border-on-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-5 font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-all">
                        Our Team
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
